- Right-click on the Databases - New Database - Database Name - Ok
- Right-click on the Tables - New - Table - Exit - Yes - Table Name - Ok or
- Right-click on the Tables - New - Table - Ctrl + S - Talen Name - Ok

*** To design the table columns and datatypes ***
- Right-click on the table - Design 

*** To enter the data into the columns ***
- Right-click on the table - Edit Top 200 Raws

*** To make the primary key increase one by one make the ID column datatype serial OR
To have the primary key increase sequentially, set the data type of the ID column to 'serial'***
- Right-click on the table - Design - Column Properties - Identity Spesification - (Is Identity) - Yes
